> "Yo, Legacy, Night Shift here, and he's in the house. Lemme know what ya want me ta do and I'm as good as there."

There's a slight pause and then Legacy's icy cold tones could be heard
across the encrypted Maximal channel, "Lord Perseus is currently the
senior officer in charge of this mission, and I will defer to his
direction."

After another pause Legacy continued, "I believe that lights are soon
to be activated. Perhaps he will require your assistance there."
